        "class": "",
        "text": "4. behind the city—is rendered (Jos 8:9), \"on the west side of Ai.\"",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Matthew Poole's Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "He commanded them; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " the same party last spoken of, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:3",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:3",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", even the five thousand mentioned ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:12",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:12",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". This historical-narration seems obscure and intricate, and at first view to make three parties, one of thirty thousand, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:3",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:3",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; one of five thousand, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:12",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:12",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", which may seem to be two several ambushes; and a third of all the people, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:5,11",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:5",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ",11",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". But if it be more narrowly and considerately observed, it will appear that there are only two parties engaged in the taking of Ai, and but one ambush, as plainly appears by comparing ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:9",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:9",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (which manifestly speaks of that party which is mentioned ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:3",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:3",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") with ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:12",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:12",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", which speaks only of five thousand, which is justly supposed to be a part of those thirty thousand named ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:3",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:3",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and that part which was to lie in ambush; unless we will suppose that there were two ambushes, one of thirty thousand, and the other of five thousand, both lying in wait in the same quarter, even ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "between Beth-el and Ai",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", on the west side of Ai, the only place where the ambush lay, as is said both ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:9,12,13",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:9",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ",12,13",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", which seems absurd and incredible. And besides, in the execution of this command, there is mention but of one ambush, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:12-14,19",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:12-14",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ",19",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and they are said to consist only of five thousand, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:12",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:12",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and they only take and burn the city, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:19",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:19",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; so that the other supposed ambush of thirty thousand is perfectly vanished and lost, and did nothing in this work; which also is very improbable. And therefore that thirty thousand, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:3",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:3",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", are the same who are called ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "the people",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "the people of war that were with Joshua",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:5,11",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:5",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ",11",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", which is pitched on the north side of Ai, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Joshua 8:11,13",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 8:11",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ",13",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", as the ambush did on the west side; but for any other side of the city, or a third party placed elsewhere about Ai, we read not one word; and therefore it may well be presumed there were no more employed to take it. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
